Bh6 d4 {and now} 15. Qxd4 $1 ({Instead, the timid} 15. Bxf8 Qxf8 16. Qxd4 Nc6
17. Qd2 Qg7 {leaves White only with a tiny advantage.}) 15... e5 16. Qd2 Re8
