Rb8 ({Black's position does not look appealing after} 13... Nh5 14. Bxg7 Nxg7
15. Ne3 bxc4 16. bxc4 Rb8 17. Rab1 Qc7 18. Qc3 {Mekhitarian,K - Fernandez,M
