only prepares the finachetto but also covers the weak Pc4 in advance.} (8. d5
Na5 9. Nd2 c5 {might lead to the so-called Yugoslav variation, that can also
be reached via 6...c5 7.Nc3 Nc6 8.d5 Na5.}) ({As was mentioned before, there
