a4 {Black fails to develop any active play on the queenside and has to sit and
wait. The play might continue:} Ne6 13. Nxe6 Bxe6 14. e4 Nd7 15. Bb2 Qa5 16.
Qc2 Rfc8 17. Nd5 Bxd5 18. exd5 $14 {with annoying pressure along the e-file.})
11. Bb2 a6 12. Qd2 Qc7 ({Hardly better was} 12... Qa5 13. Rfd1 b5 14. Nd5 Qd8
15. Rac1 bxc4 16. Nxf6+ Bxf6 17. Rxc4 $14) 13. Rac1 Qb8 14. Nd5 Nxd5 15. cxd5
