Qxd4 13. Qxd4 Bxd4 14. Rd1 Be5 15. Bh6 Bg7 16. Bxg7 Kxg7 17. Nxd6 $14 {White
regains the pawn and retains the pressure.}) {Here I found a promising new idea
} 13. Bh6 $5 $146 Rd8 ({After} 13... Re8 14. b4 Bf5 15. c5 dxc5 16. bxc5 Qd8
17. Nd6 $16 {Black cannot avoid the major loss of material.}) 14. b4 Nc7 15.
