dozen of games. I found a new natural idea:} 17. Rxe6 $146 Qxe6 18. Bc3 Qxc4
19. Qd2 Ne6 (19... Bf5 20. g4 Be4 21. Qxd6 $18) 20. Qxd6 Qc5 21. Qd3 {Black
can hardly withstand such an attack for long.}) ({Deserving of some attention
is} 12... d5 $5 {, that might invite interesting complications:} 13. cxd5 cxd5
14. Nxd5 Nfxe4 15. Bxe4 Rxe4 ({But not} 15... Bxd4 $2 16. Qc4 $1 $18 {Bocharov,
