15. Bf4 Rb6 (15... Ne5 16. Nxe5 dxe5 17. Bg5 Be6 18. Nd5 Bxd5 19. cxd5 {
looked practically lost from strategic point of view in Matamoros Franco,C -
Vocaturo,D Bratto 2008}) 16. a4 $1 bxc4 17. bxc4 Ne5 18. Nxe5 dxe5 19. Bg5 {
with a huge positional advantage.}) 13. Nde2 b5 {This move invites interesting
